Package: biotooltips
Title: Bio Tooltips for R Markdown and HTML Reports
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Matthew J.", "Meier", email = "matthew.james.meier@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Lightweight helpers for adding Bio Tooltips gene and chemical
    tooltips to R Markdown, Quarto, Shiny, pkgdown, and other HTML outputs.
    The package emits small HTML spans with module-specific data attributes
    and attaches the underlying JavaScript and CSS assets from the
    'bio-tooltips' JavaScript package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/mattjmeier/biotooltips
BugReports: https://github.com/mattjmeier/biotooltips/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    htmltools,
    jsonlite,
    knitr,
    utils
Suggests:
    DT,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
